  "name": "Metrics of diabetes risk are only minimally improved by exercise training in postmenopausal breast cancer survivors",
  "author": {
    "name": "Richard Viskochil",
    "givenName": "Richard",
    "familyName": "Viskochil",
    "affiliation": {
